		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">辉龙至多进行2段攻击：身转一周，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">40%</span><span>伤害，而后顺带将碗内的浓汤倒出，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">50%</span><span>伤害，洒在地上留下的浓汤将持续一段时间，并造成</span><span color="#ff9999">30%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/熔岩辉龙像.assets/Image_21.png')" x="1391" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/熔岩辉龙像.assets/Image_22.png')" x="1392" y="713">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/熔岩辉龙像.assets/Image_23.png')" x="1391" y="1001">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/熔岩辉龙像.assets/Image_24.png')" x="720" y="714">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/熔岩辉龙像.assets/Image_25.png')" x="719" y="1001">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/熔岩辉龙像.assets/Image_26.png')" x="719" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="399" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，辉龙装弹，准备进行迫击：抛出4-5颗汤圆，均造成<span color="#ff9999">30%,<br/>4.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">辉龙进行蓄力，而后喷吐燃素熔流，顺时针自转一圈，造成<span color="#ff9999">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1087" width="438" height="229" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">辉龙具有2种状态：「岩之人」和「熔焰之龙」；两个状态可互相转化，且受到<span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>伤害均会累积热量，但后者受到</span><span color="#99ffff">冰元素</span><span>或</span><span color="#7fbfff">水元素</span><span>伤害时会失去大量热量，直至回退「岩之人」状态。「熔焰之龙」状态下累积热量达50%和100%时，均会损失当前</span><span color="#ffbfbf">15%</span><span>生命值，而后者将瘫痪13s，苏醒后回退至「岩之人」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">辉龙进行3段攻击：分别使用左右岩壳进行攻击，依次造成<span color="#ff9999">40%,60%</span><span>伤害，最后使岩泉横流，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1087" width="422" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，辉龙搓着岩壳朝玩家方向推进，接触造成<span color="#ff9999">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">辉龙用力重击，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">30%</span><span>伤害，随后借力跃起至玩家上方，然后重重下落，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#a3320c" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#a3320c">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
