				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">瘫痪</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1128" width="442" height="212" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">深渊抗性：正常150%，熔焰状态<span color="#ff9999">火150% </span><span>/ 其他45%，瘫痪10%。<br/>热量：「岩之人」状态下350点；「熔焰之龙」状态下800点，且初始拥有</span><span color="#ffdfbf">12.5%</span><span>(100)的热量，自身常驻</span><span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>。<br/>「岩之人」状态下受到</span><span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>攻击后，会根据火元素的量积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">6.786n%</span><span>(23.75n)或</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2%</span><span>(7)热量，攒满后进入「熔焰之龙」状态；<br/>「熔焰之龙」状态下受到</span><span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>攻击后，会根据火元素的量积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2.969n%</span><span>(23.75n)或</span><span color="#ffdfbf">0.875%</span><span>(7)热量，该状态下一旦受</span><span color="#99ffff">冰元素</span><span>或</span><span color="#7fbfff">水元素</span><span>攻击时，会立即失去</span><span color="#ffdfbf">18.75%</span><span>(150)热量，热量不足会退回「岩之人」状态。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
